snippet.title: Action | Drive Angry(2/3) (2011) | The Account from hell punished a violence man
snippet.description:
(HD) portrait / vertical mode
Starring: Nicolas Cage, Amber Heard, William Fichtner, Billy Burke, Charlotte Ross
Movie Description:
Dead John Milton (Nicolas Cage) witnessed the murder of his daughter and the kidnapping of his granddaughter by Jonah King, who plans to sacrifice Milton's granddaughter, believing it will unleash Hell on Earth. Milton stole Satan's gun of Godkiller and escaped from hell for revenge.
